## Proactive Use

- Before multi-file changes: read skills/plan.md
- Before committing: read skills/pre-commit-check.md
- After implementing: read skills/verify.md
- End of session: read skills/session-protocol.md
- When build fails: read skills/build-fix.md
- On dirty worktree: read skills/dirty-guard.md
- Session start: read skills/run-tagging.md
